F0\"| [[Ribnik, Bosnia and Herzegovina|Ribnik]]\n| align=\"right\"| 5\n| align=\"right\"| \n| align=\"right\"| 1\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\" | [[Srbac]]\n| align=\"right\" | 1\n| align=\"right\" | \n| align=\"right\" | 1\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\" | [[Srebrenica]]\n| align=\"right\" | 1\n| align=\"right\" | \n| align=\"right\" | 0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\" | [[\u0160ekovi\u0107i]]\n| align=\"right\" | 1\n| align=\"right\" | \n| align=\"right\" | 0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\" | [[\u0160ipovo]]\n| align=\"right\" | 11\n| align=\"right\" | \n| align=\"right\" | 0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\" | [[Tesli\u0107]]\n| align=\"right\" | 14\n| align=\"right\" | \n| align=\"right\" | 1\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\" | [[Trebinje]]\n| align=\"right\" | 10\n| align=\"right\" | \n| align=\"right\" | 0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\" | [[Zvornik]]\n| align=\"right\" | 1\n| align=\"right\" | \n| align=\"right\" | 0\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" align=\"right\"| Total\n! align=\"right\"| 453\n! align=\"right\"| 14\n! align=\"right\"| 179\n|-\n| colspan=\"5\"|{{small|''As of 14 April 2020''}}<ref name=\"JZU Institut za javno zdravstvo RS\" /><ref name=\"koronausrpskoj\" />\n|}\n\nAs of 14 April 2020, people from following [[Cantons of the Federation of Bosnia and Herzegovina|cantons]] and municipalities in the Federation of Bosnia and Herzegovina have been infected:\n\n{| class=\"sortable wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | Canton\n! scope=\"col\" | Municipalities affected\n! scope=\"col\" | Cases\n! scope=\"col\" | Deaths\n! scope=\"col\" | Recoveries<ref name=\"covid-19.ba\" />\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\"| [[Canton 10]]\n| align=\"left\"| [[Livno]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.livno-online.com/zupanija/34890-prvi-slucaj-korona-virusa-u-livnu |title=Prvi slu\u010daj korona virusa u Livnu |last=User |first=Super |website=Livno Online |language=hr-hr |access-date=4 April 2020}}</ref>\n| align=\"right\"| 25\n| align=\"right\"| 1\n| align=\"right\"| 0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\"| [[Bosnian-Podrinje Canton Gora\u017ede|Bosnian-Podrinje Canton]]\n| align=\"left\"| [[Gora\u017ede]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://faktor.ba/vijest/prvi-slucaj-u-gorazdu-svi-koji-su-bili-u-kontaktu-sa-direktoricom-ginexa-moraju-se-javiti-na-broj-121-/74984 |title=Prvi slu\u010daj u Gora\u017edu: Svi koji su bili u kontaktu sa direktoricom Ginexa moraju se javiti na broj 121 |website=www.faktor.ba |language=bs-BA}}</ref>\n| align=\"right\"| 11\n| align=\"right\"| 0\n| align=\"right\"| 3\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\"| [[Central Bosnia Canton]]\n| align=\"left\"| [[Bugojno]],<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.klix.ba/vijesti/bih/potvrdjeno-jos-devet-pozitivnih-na-koronavirus-u-hercegovini-i-srednjoj-bosni/200403031 |title=Potvr\u0111eno jo\u0161 devet pozitivnih na koronavirus u Hercegovini i srednjoj Bosni |website=Klix.ba |language=bs-BA |access-date=3 April 2020}}</ref> [[Gornji Vakuf-Uskoplje]],<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.bugojno-danas.info/prvi-slucaj-zaraze-korona-virusom-u-gornjem-vakufu-uskoplju/ |title=Prvi slu\u010daj zaraze Korona virusom u Gornjem Vakufu-Uskoplju |website=Bugojno-danas.info |language=bs-BA |access-date=30 March 2020}}</ref> [[Kiseljak]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Prvi pozitivan slu\u010daj korona virusa u Kiseljaku |url=https://www.artinfo.ba/index.php/vijesti/24422-prvi-pozitivan-slucaj-korona-virusa-u-kiseljaku |website=ARTinfo |accessdate=13 April 2020 |language=hr-hr}}</ref>, [[Novi Travnik]],<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.klix.ba/vijesti/bih/soliter-u-novom-travniku-pod-blokadom-zbog-zarazenog-muskarca-obustavljen-rad-bnt-a/200322053 |title=Soliter u Novom Travniku pod blokadom zbog zara\u017eenog mu\u0161karca, obustavljen rad BNT-a |website=Klix.ba |language=bs-BA |access-date=22 March 2020}}</ref> [[V