1820/http://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/sonu-ke-titu-ki-sweety-song-dil-chori-honey-singh-kartik-aaryan-nushrat-barucha-watch-video-4999236/#|archive-date=27 December 2017|url-status=live|df=dmy-all}}</ref> || Honey Singh, Simar kaur, Singhsta\n| rowspan=3|Yo Yo Honey Singh \n|-\n| | Chhote Chhote Peg  || Yo Yo Honey Singh, [[Neha Kakkar]], [[Navraj Hans]] \n|-\n| ''[[Mitron]]'' || This Party Is Over Now|| Yo Yo Honey Singh \n|-\n| ''[[Loveyatri]]'' || Rang Taari|| [[Dev Negi]], Yo Yo Honey Singh || Tanishk Bagchi\n|-\n| ''[[Baazaar]]'' || Billionaire  || Yo Yo Honey Singh, Simar kaur, Singhsta || Yo Yo Honey Singh\n|-\n|rowspan=5|2019\n|rowspan=2|''[[Jabariya Jodi]]''|| Khadke Glassy \n|rowspan=2|Yo Yo Honey Singh, [[Ashok Masti]], [[Jyotica Tangri]]\n|rowspan=2|Tanishk Bagchi, [[Ashok Masti]], Ramji Gulati\n|-\n|Glassy 2.0\n|-\n|''[[Jhootha Kahin Ka]]''||Funk Love || rowspan=2 colspan=2|Yo Yo Honey Singh\n|-\n||''[[Marjaavaan]]''|| Peeyu Datke \n<ref>{{cite news|title=Yo Yo Honey Singh \u0928\u0947 \u0915\u093f\u092f\u093e \u0916\u0941\u0932\u093e\u0938\u093e, \u091c\u0932\u094d\u0926 \u0939\u0940 \u0915\u0930\u0947\u0902\u0917\u0947 \u092c\u0921\u093c\u093e \u0927\u092e\u093e\u0915\u093e |url=https://www.infook.in/yo-yo-honey-singh/honey-singh-gave-information-about-his-upcoming-project/|accessdate=3 October 2019|publisher=INFOok|date= 26 September 2019|url-status=live|df=dmy-all}}\n</ref> \n|-\n|''[[Pagalpanti (2019 film)]]'' || Thumka <ref>{{cite news|title=\u092a\u093e\u0917\u0932\u092a\u0902\u0924\u0940 \u092b\u093f\u0932\u094d\u092e  \u2013 200 \u092c\u0948\u0915\u0905\u092a \u0921\u093e\u0902\u0938\u0930\u094d\u0938 \u0915\u0947 \u0938\u093e\u0925 \u090f\u0915 \u091f\u093e\u0907\u091f\u0932 \u0938\u0949\u0928\u094d\u0917 \u0939\u0948.|url=https://www.infook.in/\u092f\u094b-\u092f\u094b-\u0939\u0928\u0940-\u0938\u093f\u0902\u0939/\u0939\u0928\u0940-\u0938\u093f\u0902\u0939/\u092a\u093e\u0917\u0932\u092a\u0902\u0924\u0940-\u092b\u093f\u0932\u094d\u092e-200-\u092c\u0948\u0915\u0905\u092a-\u0921\u093e/|accessdate=24 October 2019|publisher=INFOok|date= 24 April 2019|url-status=live|df=dmy-all}}\n</ref>  || Yo Yo Honey Singh || Yo Yo Honey Singh\n\n|}\n\n== Filmography ==\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"margin: 1em 1em 1em 0; background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px #aaa solid; border-collapse: collapse;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"4\" border=\"2\"  \n|+ '''Feature films as an actor'''\n|- bgcolor=\"#AAAAACCCCDDDDD\" align=\"centre\"\n! Year\n! Film\n! Role\n! Language\n! class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n|-\n| rowspan=1| 2012 || ''[[Mirza - The Untold Story]]''|| Deesha || Punjabi ||\n|-\n| rowspan=1| 2013 || ''[[Tu Mera 22 Main Tera 22]]'' || Rolly || Punjabi || \n|-\n| rowspan=1| 2014 || ''[[The Xpose]]'' || Kenny Damania || Hindi ||\n|-\n| rowspan=1| 2016 || ''[[Zorawar]]'' || Agent Zorawar Singh || Punjabi || \n|}\n\n== Awards ==\n\n* ETC award for the Best Sound in 2006 for song \"Glassi\"{{citation needed|date=April 2018}}\n* PTC award for the Best Folk Pop Award 2009 for album ''Rebirth''{{citation needed|date=April 2018}}\n*[[PTC Punjabi]] Best Music Director 2010 for song \"Desi Daroo\"<ref>[http://www.tribuneindia.com/2010/20100310/jplus.htm#4 PTC Punjabi Music Awards 2010] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100515194942/http://www.tribuneindia.com/2010/20100310/jplus.htm#4#4 |date=15 May 2010 }}. ''The Tribune''. Retrieved 3 January 2012.</ref>\n*[[PTC Punjabi]] Best Music Director 2011 for album ''The Folkstar''<ref>[http://ptcpmusicawards.com/winner.php PTC 2011 music award Winners List] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120115155128/http://ptcpmusicawards.com/winner.php# |date=15 January 2012 }}. Ptcpmusicawards.com. Retrieved 3 January 2012.</ref><ref>[http://www.cinepunjab.com/2011/03/ptc-music-awards-2011.html PTC Music Awards 2011 List of Awards Winners] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120502023602/http://www.cinepunjab.com/2011/03/ptc-music-awards-2011.html# |date=2 May 2012 }}. Cinepunjab.com (18 November 2011). Retrieved 3 January 2012.</ref>\n*[[PTC Punjabi]] Best Music Director 2012 for album ''I.V.'' (''[[International Villager]]'')<ref>[http://ptcpmusicawards.com/winners.html PTC 2012 music award Winners List] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121106110130/http://ptcpmusicawards.com/winners.html# |date=6 November 2012 }} Ptcpmusicawards.com. Retrieved 25 March 2012.</ref>\n*BritAsia Best International Act 2012<ref>[http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2012-10-10/music/34364818_1_music-awards-lifetime-achievement-award-biggest-event BritAsia Music Awards winners] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131219035420/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2012-10-10/music/34364818_1_music-awards-lifetime-achievement-award-biggest-event# |date=19 December 2013 }} ''The Times of India''. Retrieved 1 December 2012.</ref>\n*[[UK Asian Music Awards]] Best International Album 2012 for Album album ''I.V.'' (''[[International Villager]]'')<ref>[http://www.chakdey.com/lebara-mobile-uk-asian-music-awards-ukama-results Lebara Mobile UK Asian Music Awards (UKAMA 2012) Results] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121030115943/http://www.chakdey.com/lebara-mobile-uk-asian-music-awards-ukama-results/# |date=30 October 2012 }} chakdey.com. Retrieved 1 December 2012.</ref>\n*[[PTC Punjabi]] Film Award&nbsp;\u2013  Best Music Director 2012 for ''[[Mirza&nbsp;\u2013 The Untold Story]]''<ref name=\"ptc\">[http://www.ptcpunjabifilmawards.com/winers.html PTC Punjabi Film Award (PTCPFA 2013) Results] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130804223425/http://www.ptcpunjabifilmawards.com/winers.html# |date=4 August 2013 }}. Retrieved 22 March 2013.</ref>\n*[[PTC Punjabi]] Film Award&nbsp;\u2013 Best Debut (Male) for ''[[Mirza&nbsp;\u2013 The Untold Story]]''<ref name=\"ptc\" />\n*[[MTV]] VMAI Awards&nbsp;\u2013 Best Indie Artist (male) 2013 for song \"Brown Rang\"<ref>[