n|Iraq}} '''[[Iraq]]'''<ref name=\"guardian1017\">{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/oct/17/iraqi-forces-begin-assault-on-isis-stronghold-mosul |title=Mosul offensive: forces launch mass attack on Iraqi city in bid to oust Isis |first1=Martin |last1=Chulov |first2=Hannah |last2=Summers |work=[[The Guardian]] |date=17 October 2016 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161017145243/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/oct/17/iraqi-forces-begin-assault-on-isis-stronghold-mosul |archivedate=17 October 2016 |df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n* {{flagicon|Kurdistan}} [[Iraqi Kurdistan]]\n{{flagicon image|Seal of Combined Joint Task Force \u2013 Operation Inherent Resolve.svg|size=25px|border=}} '''[[Combined Joint Task Force \u2013 Operation Inherent Resolve|CJTF\u2013OIR]]'''\n* {{flag|United States}}<ref name=\"guardian1017\" />\n* {{flag|France}}<ref name=\"guardian1017\" />\n* {{flag|United Kingdom}}<ref name=\"guardian1017\" />\n* {{flag|Canada}}<ref name=\"Canadatroops\">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/harjit-sajjan-supporting-troops-iraq-1.3809333 |title=Canadian troops supporting Kurds in fight to free Mosul from ISIS |first=Lee |last=Berthiaume |publisher=CBC News |date=17 October 2016 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161018094059/http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/harjit-sajjan-supporting-troops-iraq-1.3809333 |archivedate=18 October 2016 |df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n* {{flag|Australia}}<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.skynews.com.au/news/top-stories/2016/10/17/australia-to-have-role-in-battle-for-mosul.html |title=Australia to have role in battle for Mosul |publisher=Sky News Australia |date=17 October 2016 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161018205626/http://www.skynews.com.au/news/top-stories/2016/10/17/australia-to-have-role-in-battle-for-mosul.html |archivedate=18 October 2016 |df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n* {{flag|Germany}}<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.alaraby.co.uk/english/news/2016/9/24/germany-will-take-part-in-the-battle-for-mosul |title=Germany 'will take part in the battle for Mosul' |work=Al-Araby Al-Jadeed (The New Arab) |date=24 September 2016 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220064908/https://www.alaraby.co.uk/english/news/2016/9/24/germany-will-take-part-in-the-battle-for-mosul |archivedate=20 December 2016 |df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n* {{flag|Turkey}}<ref name=\"aj1023\" />\n* {{flag|Netherlands}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.defensie.nl/actueel/nieuws/2019/12/20/23-militairen-onderscheiden-voor-uitzonderlijke-inzet-tijdens-missies|title=23 Militairen onderscheiden voor uitzonderlijke inzet tijdens missies|last=|first=|date=19 December 2019|website=Defensie|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref>\n{{flag|Iran}}<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.csmonitor.com/World/Middle-East/2016/1029/What-role-is-Iran-playing-in-the-Mosul-offensive |title=What role is Iran playing in the Mosul offensive? |first=David |last=Iaconangelo\n|work=[[Christian Science Monitor]] |date=29 October 2016 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161107232617/http://www.csmonitor.com/World/Middle-East/2016/1029/What-role-is-Iran-playing-in-the-Mosul-offensive |archivedate=7 November 2016 |df=dmy-all}}</ref><br />'''Supported by:'''<br />{{flag|Pakistan}}<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.dawn.com/news/1345432/pakistan-helped-iraq-in-defeating-is-says-iraqi-envoy |title=Archived copy |access-date=10 February 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190212070604/https://www.dawn.com/news/1345432/pakistan-helped-iraq-in-defeating-is-says-iraqi-envoy |archive-date=12 February 2019 |url-status=live |df=dmy-all}}</ref><br />{{flag|Hezbollah}}<ref name=\"Hezbollah\">{{cite news |url=http://www.longwarjournal.org/archives/2016/11/hezbollah-fighters-train-iraqi-shiite-militants-near-mosul.php |title=Hezbollah fighters train Iraqi Shiite militants near Mosul |first=David |last=Daoud |work=[[Lo